| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6795 — Recovery Inhibition (lynx)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 16d4a3d2-87d7-582e-822b-98a5ff9e80c6"
